##It's the epidemic they're trying to avoid. It's the agency

Micro-signal Jianjiaobuluo

Function description, pepper tribe, amplify your voice! Chinese Women Workers Exclusive Information Platform, you are welcome to pay attention!

The author, Shi Hongli, brings the story of four domestic workers.

Notice her initial description of the beautiful world of single apartment rentals: So detailed, so digital -- a place they call home.

Behind the simple luggage and bed is a sprawling map of China: Snow in Yanqing District, two days and nights in a sorghum field, weeds to be weeded in a scenic and economically backward Sansu-ri.

As space unfolds, so does time. But as time goes by, make these years more than 50, what have suffered from the female fear of things, unexpectedly no less. It's the epidemic they're trying to avoid. It's the agency.

As a writing director, contributing editor: Far Away

The author, Shi Hongli, brings the story of four domestic workers.

Notice her initial description of the beautiful world of single apartment rentals: So detailed, so digital -- a place they call home.

Behind the simple luggage and bed is a sprawling map of China: Snow in Yanqing District, two days and nights in a sorghum field, weeds to be weeded in a scenic and economically backward Sansu-ri.

As space unfolds, so does time. But as time goes by, make these years more than 50, what have suffered from the female fear of things, unexpectedly no less. It's the epidemic they're trying to avoid. It's the agency.

As a writing director, contributing editor: Far Away

Outside the East Fifth Ring Road Lies Urban Village, Florida, Pys, Beijing Capital International Airport, near the village. Get off from the bus stop, walk about ten minutes, there is a single apartment building called the better world. The building is full of tenements, with four tenants in room 201. This apartment is about 20 square meters, with kitchen and bathroom, two 1.5 beds, a small closet, a writing desk. The monthly rent is 1,200 yuan, the sanitation is 20 yuan, the electricity is calculated according to one yuan once, the annual heating fee is 1,200 yuan, the Wifi is 50 yuan per month. All the expenses were split among four people.

These four are domestic workers, are the sister-in-law Zhao Hongmei, Li Aiju, Qian Guilan, and child-raising sister-in-law Zhou Chunyue. After the eighth day of the first lunar month in previous years, most of them worked as domestic helpers for their employers to earn money. This year, eight days after the Lantern Festival, three of them are still indoors: In quarantine and unemployed. And Not in the house of that, named Qian Guilan, because his hometown closed village road, now also can not come out.

(the images in this article are provided by the author without explanation.)
The maids didn't know each other very well. Domestic Service companies all have wechat groups, each aunt has multiple groups of domestic service, the company takes the intermediary fee is too high (generally, take 30% of the salary, high take 50% , every month to take) , so we have to force people to take jobs in different intermediary companies wechat groups in private, dream of finding the company with the lowest finder's fee. Active in these groups, they come and go, and they get to know each other.
Through Wechat, like-minded aunts put it all together: Let's rent.
Many domestic workers live in domestic service companies, which has many drawbacks. Because domestic service companies provide accommodation for aunts, the corresponding, aunts have to work in the company; in company accommodation, we meet every day, some domestic service companies in the guise of training, repeatedly collect training fees, if aunt refused, company Ostracism; The accommodation provided by domestic service agencies is poor and requires a fee.
And oneself rent a house, one is freedom, can look for a job to different company, sometimes can escape company to draw intermediary fee, occasionally contact illicit work to earn more money, two still can sleep comfortable some at night.
Some employers want to get out of this situation and don't want to spend the money because the company takes the finder's fee and both parties take it. They also often contact their aunts privately to save money on intermediary fees. Domestic Workers Mobility, domestic companies do not want to assume responsibility, not to aunt protection, so do not sign a contract with aunt. So when aunties do this, the housekeeping company doesn't care, and certainly doesn't have the right to.

One
Sister-in-law Zhao Hongmei was moved in last June, is a Sichuan sister-in-law, speak simply straightforward. Used to live in a company dorm. snores a little. The housemaster didn't like it, often scolded it, said it affected other people's rest.

Chiu hung-mui just got a job. In fact, I wasn't going to take orders during the festival. I wanted to take my daughter to Yanqing District to enjoy the snow. Daughter rare snow, said, did not look. The plan did not change quickly, when the company told customers near the Spring Festival, Zhao Hongmei thought, or on it.
Husband at home has COPD, loss of ability to work, and every day to breathe oxygen, drug. In the early years, the family built two small buildings, which were not in line with the preferential targets of the state in poverty alleviation. In addition to the new rural cooperative medical service reimbursing part of the medical expenses, the other expenses were all at their own expense. All these years, they earned some hard-earned money by making Hongmei as a matchmaker's wife, to support my husband's medical bills and the family's basic expenses. So when you see a chance to make some money, you can't miss it. There's plenty of time for everything else.
To be precise, Zhao Hongmei knew that the new crown pneumonia or the day of the city closure in Wuhan, baby mother told her. Before she did not go to the door, accidentally from Baidu browsing on a look, said that is a rumor, daily for livelihood, also did not put the mind on this. Month sister-in-law is a high salary, strict requirements, do not look at mobile phones, it is said that mobile phone radiation on the health of the newborn, unless there is an important matter, usually put on mute, after 22 pm, can see 20 minutes of Wechat or Baidu information. Of course, overwork every day, people just want to sleep, how time close to the phone.
Whether the epidemic is serious or not, Zhao Hongmei is a large part of the mouth from the baby father that every day from the supermarket, the district will bring back some stories. The blue-suited man and the white-capped woman vie for the Tomato; the big sister with a northeast accent complains that the price of Chinese cabbage exceeds that of eggs; the liver and kidney that the baby mother has to eat can not be bought; express delivery is not allowed to enter the community; the community begins to measure body temperature; the community begins to register, the community only allowed two days out to buy food, the community began to close management..
The other part of the message came from news of the outbreak on mobile phones and from the hanting hotel across the street. Zhao Hongmei opens the window twice a day in the morning and in the afternoon. Traffic was heavy at the entrance of the hotel before the city was shut down. After the city was sealed, there was no one left. The signs are that the epidemic is getting worse.

Domestic sisters in the group every day to pass information on the epidemic, take body temperature, punch cards, hair location. Zhao Hongmei did the same, as proof of her health and not leaving Beijing.
The 26-day contract period is coming soon, and Zhao Hongmei is going to leave the account. The Baby Daddy brings back the story: The control is more and more strict, the community does not allow the tenant to enter. She began to worry about accommodation and contacted the landlord to ask if she could return to the rental house. The landlord gave an ambiguous answer. A said, to social security card, but this is for her Scheherazade, which agency will help Yuesao to buy social security? Two said, can take a chance, let the company seal proof did not leave Beijing. I do not know is that the agency does not have a company seal, or no business license, Zhao Hongmei anyway did not cover the company seal, she was embarrassed.

Without the company seal, her credentials are a piece of paper. Punch card, friends circle positioning, village workers will not admit that, because not leave Beijing, can not provide health certificates back to Beijing, can not open the quarantine card. She's at a client's house, and the landlord has no record of her leaving Beijing, and she doesn't have a name, and she can't provide a social security card.
Zhao Hongmei dumb eat Coptis, a basket of good words said, night fell, the village staff agreed, can only enter not out. Once you're out, you can't come in. Just rest, do your country a favor, and make money when this epidemic is over. Now she has been working for a week, waiting for the day the quarantine was lifted, out to look for work.

Two
Qian Guilan and Zhao Hongmei are fellow townsmen, their registered permanent residence, beautiful scenery, backward economy. Qian Guilan stature short, voice and mosquitoes similar, thin voice, do farm work is a pair of loss phase. Her life is really hard to read.
In 1983, all 56 children in the brigade took the exam for junior high school. Only 5 children were admitted to the exam. Another 5 children chose to repeat their studies. The remaining 46 children graduated from the local primary school, including Qian Guilan. At the beginning of the Household-responsibility system, Qian Guilan worked as a farmer all day long. At 19, she was kidnapped and sold to Shanxi by traffickers. In her words, she also wanted to marry and live a good life in Shanxi. In addition to being deceived by traffickers, she also dreamed of a rich outside world, i hate the mountains in South Sichuan.
The outside world is very helpless, Shanxi in addition to living in caves, not washing feet in winter, poor and Sichuan is no different. Shanxi men afraid she ran out of both money and people, strict custody and regular abuse. The next year she gave birth to a little boy. In the third year, when the sorghum was booming, one night she saw an opportunity to escape.
Mother-in-law carrying the children in front of the chase, Shanxi men with the torch of the village with the male relatives followed. Qian Guilan hid in the sorghum field for two days and one night before daring to come out. She begged all the way, doing odd jobs, some words can not describe the work, fled back home. After remarriage, she gave birth to a son and a daughter. Her husband works as a security guard in a small community in Chengdu with a limited salary.
Qian Guilan worked hard to save money and gave 50,000 yuan to her eldest son in Shanxi in 2015 as a wedding gift. The mother and the baby break the ice.

After the closure of the village, Chien Guilan led her son, a college student, a high school daughter, and a security guard husband, to the fields of Florida, picking weeds taller than people and sawing trees thicker than the mouth of a bowl. Flatten the fields and give them to the old people in the village to grow crops, fruits and vegetables. She could get some food subsidies, at least without being fined. Because the captain said there's GonNa be a fine.
More often than not, she's just waiting for the inflection point to come up and the outbreak to go away. Out there, it is better to leave one's husband and child behind, to grovel and look at people's faces to earn a wage than to go hungry in a village. The family can not feed themselves on three Mu and six fen of cultivated land.

Every now and then, in the rental room, she would say, I was like Gao Jialin. By the village party secretary's son, otherwise, I'd still be teaching.

Zhou Chunyue to Beijing, first do nanny, after the rise of the month sister-in-law occupation, turn to do month sister-in-law. Moon sister-in-law's job is mainly to stay up late. When it comes to high demand babies, as William defines them, sleep only three or four hours a day. Zhou Chunyue suffers from slight anemia. After staying up late, she walks during the day and looks like she is drunk from afar. Once, too sleepy, holding the baby, a bump, hit the guardrail of the crib. Crib guardrail has a layer of sponge collision device, little baby is not a problem, baby grandma can not, pull her to hit the door, let her taste the taste of being hit. Customers also complained that she worked hard for 18 days, 7600 yuan of hard-earned money on such a bubble.
In fact, the housekeeping company lost only 1,000 yuan, and the remaining 6,600 yuan was swindled by the housekeeping company. The salary of month-old sister-in-law is collected by the domestic service company, which gives the false impression that the employee system and the interests of the clients are guaranteed. Domestic workers complain of no way, can only comfort themselves, bad luck, give money to avoid disaster.
Now she's a baby sister, usually after three months. The money is less than the money she earns, but she can rest at night.

Photograph: Coconut
Three years ago, Zhou resigned from her last client's home. She worked for two months: her employer made her eat scraps every day, and she kept quiet. Later, when there wasn't enough to eat, she quit. A week before her resignation, Zhou began contacting a domestic service company, hoping the company would help her keep an eye out for suitable childcare clients.
Zhou Chunyue culture is high, have experience, relatively easy to go to households. Spring Festival is also a shortage of domestic workers. The housekeeping company found a client for her and took her in years later. During the Spring Festival, she returned to her hometown and the epidemic spread all over China. On the second day of the first lunar month, she set off for Beijing. She wants to leave home as soon as possible, in addition to the domestic service company does not want to cook the ducks fly away, hurry to urge her to go to the house, the fear of domestic violence husband is another reason.
Back in Beijing, there was no quarantine policy, she went straight to the door. Four days at a client's house, and then they tighten up. The client is an elementary school teacher, and his hours have been delayed. Then the client started to find fault, find excuses, in fact, love money. Eventually, she was forced out. And her four-day salary doesn't even cover the finder's fee.

Five
The housemaid sisters in this House are in a good frame of mind and open to all things. They thought of the sisters who had been trapped in their hometown and felt better now. Some sisters just came to Beijing, domestic service companies do not allow to live in the afternoon to go home, home to quarantine. Another sister came to Beijing to spend 2,000 yuan, in the hotel isolation, after isolation, many units did not resume work, the customer home is not short of manpower, also can not find a job, no place to go, in and out of difficulties.
The three stay in the "better world" domestic worker sisters, usually too busy, now free, in addition to focus on the epidemic and follow the drama, learning has become their first task. Mother and Child Care Knowledge, early childhood education, cooking skills, should be systematically learned to improve themselves is necessary.
From nanny to sister-in-law, to the age of destiny, we know that eventually will be eliminated. Now, most employers have cameras in their homes, some of them perverts, even in their bathrooms. Unscrupulous domestic firms and clients are not alone. In addition to Home Economics Company back pay, run away, there are some home economics company, in the aunt is about to leave the house, colludes with the employer, let the employer nitpick. That's how they ended up ganging up on domestic workers'hard-earned money.
So, every time you have a suitable job as a housekeeper, you feel lucky. For most domestic worker sisters, domestic service income is their only source of income.
Those of you who are going to work, you must cherish the opportunity to work, as soon as you enter the home of a client to replace a new mask, out of their own disinfectant, wipe hands, wipe the suitcase, bath, change all clothes. After all, says Fote, there is nothing more important than a paycheck.

Some sisters just came to Beijing, domestic service companies do not allow to live in the afternoon to go home, home to quarantine. Another sister came to Beijing to spend 2,000 yuan, in the hotel isolation, after isolation, many units did not resume work, the customer home is not short of manpower, also can not find a job, no place to go, in and out of difficulties.

The three stay in the "better world" domestic worker sisters, usually too busy, now free, in addition to focus on the epidemic and follow the drama, learning has become their first task. Mother and Child Care Knowledge, early childhood education, cooking skills, should be systematically learned to improve themselves is necessary.

From nanny to sister-in-law, to the age of destiny, we know that eventually will be eliminated. Now, most employers have cameras in their homes, some of them perverts, even in their bathrooms. Unscrupulous domestic firms and clients are not alone. In addition to Home Economics Company back pay, run away, there are some home economics company, in the aunt is about to leave the house, colludes with the employer, let the employer nitpick. That's how they ended up ganging up on domestic workers'hard-earned money.

So, every time you have a suitable job as a housekeeper, you feel lucky. For most domestic worker sisters, domestic service income is their only source of income.

Those of you who are going to work, you must cherish the opportunity to work, as soon as you enter the home of a client to replace a new mask, out of their own disinfectant, wipe hands, wipe the suitcase, bath, change all clothes. After all, says Fote, there is nothing more important than a paycheck.
